7fc4d98e903cc8091cc61166e2fbb10aac304a3a","tid":409100,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T18:58:31.000Z","msg":"如果今日係apple store 買6S<br />\n咁係咪一按更新就由9.0直跳11？"},{"pid":"9b464be8b8aacf0bf8a5eefebf83f3bac08bff2d","tid":409100,"uid":59552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Apple Watch 升左無得落😭😭😭</blockquote><br />\n隻錶restore過，再用ios11 連返，佢會有一個9.x backup 揀.</blockquote><br />\n 升左 watchOS 4 都得？"},{"pid":"c35f505527a498bf1abe72b1f15837d589988195","tid":409100,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T19:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但我而家升返11都用唔返11個back up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBackup corrupted?</blockquote><br />\n唔係，佢直接skip左我個back up變新機<br />\n<br />\n我留返個back up等買左x個時再試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ec6783b2470adc8813164d51283b761816c330","tid":409100,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T23:57:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但我而家升返11都用唔返11個back up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBackup corrupted?</blockquote><br />\n唔係，佢直接skip左我個back up變新機<br />\n<br />\n我留返個back up等買左x個時再試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該咁講，當時有兩個back up(新+原有）咁我整個時佢就不停幫我整左新個backup落去，但新既入面其實無野，都唔知佢有無cover到落去，淨係知原本想整個隻就點都cover唔到落去<br />\n<br />\n而家刪哂啲新backup得返個舊既，但唔敢再試，一陣又唔掂真係食得屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f858594f16deb43406c92129f7f0cdba888d846d","tid":409100,"uid":30190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20